Fixes/Enhancement:

- Do note preload all the songs at screen_song
- Add binary dump of the songs (to speed up directory browsing)
- Add "To start" cursor before sentence beginning in more than 'n' beat
- Draw "to be sung" notes with cairo instead of SDLRectangle
  This should enable "sing" notes strech in a themed rectangle
- Use a cross platform input sound library (portAudio ?)
- Fixe install things (add a secondary theme directoryn)
